title._content: Capt. S.O. Morris, Edna Cole, Mrs. Lillian Howard, Elsie Meiser, Josephine Bartlett, Sarah Marin, Anna Holland, A. Howell, Marie Rampsperger, Millie Bartildes, Mrs. Jennie Waldis  (LOC)

description._content: Bain News Service,, publisher. Capt. S.O. Morris, Edna Cole, Mrs. Lillian Howard, Elsie Meiser, Josephine Bartlett, Sarah Marin, Anna Holland, A. Howell, Marie Rampsperger, Millie Bartildes, Mrs. Jennie Waldis [1914 July 16] 1 negative : glass ; 5 x 7 in. or smaller. Notes: Title from data provided by the Bain News Service on the negative. Photograph shows women's swimming contests at Sheepshead Bay, Brooklyn, New York City, July 16, 1914. (Source: Flickr Commons project, 2011) Forms part of: George Grantham Bain Collection (Library of Congress). Format: Glass negatives. Rights Info: No known restrictions on publication. Repository: Library of Congress, Prints and Photographs Division, Washington, D.C. 20540 USA, hdl.loc.gov/loc.pnp/pp.print General information about the Bain Collection is available at hdl.loc.gov/loc.pnp/pp.ggbain Higher resolution image is available (Persistent URL): hdl.loc.gov/loc.pnp/ggbain.16577 Call Number: LC-B2- 3149-12
